      "widgets_values": [
        "This workflow colourizes black & white photographs. It is not for faded colour restoration: use 05A for that. Generated colours are plausible estimates, not historical facts.\\n\\nFaces are not passed to CodeFormer, GFPGAN, FaceDetailer or other face generators. Keep denoise low to preserve identity and geometry.\\n\\nUse a local mask workflow for isolated colour mistakes rather than repeatedly recolourizing the whole photograph."
